\title{Neyman-Pearson Framework}
\p{Given #{\alpha \in (0,1)}. The optimal hypothesis test in the \em{Neyman-Pearson} framework is one that satisfies
##{\operatorname*{min}_{P_{Z\mid X}}\;\mathbb{P}_{H_{1}}\left(Z=0\right),\quad\mathrm{subject\,to}\quad\mathbb{P}_{H_{0}}\left(Z=1\right)\leq\alpha.}
}
